        v-model="drawer"
        class="white">
        <v-list
            dense
            nav>
            <v-list-item
                v-for="link in links"
                :key="link.text"
                :to="link.to"
                link>
                <v-list-item-icon>
                    <v-icon>{{ link.icon }}</v-icon>
                </v-list-item-icon>

                <v-list-item-content>

        </v-list>
